Package ORM.Base

Class Field

java.lang.Object
ORM.Base.Field
public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
Every database column gets represented as a field.

      private boolean ignore
      Boolean true/false if field can be ignored for database entry creation. Example: field is referencing a foreign key relation (1:1, 1:n) but does not need a foreign key entry in this table.

      Boolean true/false if field has nullable key attribute in database.
